{"Id":523780,"Title":"直路行","Dynasty":"明","Author":"何景明","Context":"直路难行，直言难受。邪径捷足，莠言悦口。直言如矢，闻者畏惮。如射曲巷，鲜不折干。直路坦坦，不可避难。大夫史鱼，死以尸谏。汲黯抗言，不冠不见。轮扁之言，桓公是悟。焦不避烹，秦皇霁怒。猛虎在前，不为我言。虺蛇在后，不为我告。二世自閟，遭害于宫。虢君怒御，枕块道中。不忍其惮，宁忍其乱。苟畏尔耻，必视尔死。如药弗溃，其疾必遂。如矢不直，不能贯革。小人恶直，君子是持。神之听之，终获其釐。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"6768d4117e390975a116b74b7ab9111a","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6416651,"Sentence":"直路难行，直言难受。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhǐ lù nán háng ，zhǐ yán nán shòu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416652,"Sentence":"邪径捷足，莠言悦口。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xié jìng jié zú ，yǒu yán yuè kǒu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416653,"Sentence":"直言如矢，闻者畏惮。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhǐ yán rú shi ，wén zhě wèi dàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416654,"Sentence":"如射曲巷，鲜不折干。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rú shè qū hàng ，xiān bú shé gān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416655,"Sentence":"直路坦坦，不可避难。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhǐ lù tǎn tǎn ，bú kě bì nán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416656,"Sentence":"大夫史鱼，死以尸谏。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dà fū shi yú ，si yi shī jiàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416657,"Sentence":"汲黯抗言，不冠不见。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jǐ àn kàng yán ，bú guān bú jiàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416658,"Sentence":"轮扁之言，桓公是悟。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lún biǎn zhī yán ，huán gōng shì wù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6416659,"Sentence":"焦不避烹，秦皇霁怒。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jiāo bú bì pēng ，qǐn huáng jì nù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"I